		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />+5V will be the top right pin, GND will be the bottom left pin.
<br />
<br />I am not a modder, but the few times I've cut ABS plastic I melted the area with an old soldering iron, then used a hot knife to clean it up.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
